Phone game base code
=====================================================================

This project is a base-code/boilerplate style project that will allow
you to bootstrap a game quickly.

Dependencies:

   SFML-2.1 (provided in the source tree)
   lua-5.2.1 (provided in the source tree)

   libgl1-mesa-dev
   libglu1-mesa-dev
   libglm-dev

SFML-2.1 is included in the source tree and if these libraries aren't
installed on the system, they'll need to be included on your libpath
before attempting execution:

export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=game/libs/SFML-2.1/lib
